\p \add вүҲCry loudly\add*, \add вүҲyou\add* shipsВҰ290092 from TarshishВҰ290093 becauseВҰ290094 your home \add port\add* has been destroyed. It's been \add вүҲreported\add* to them from KittimВҰ290100 \add (CyprusВҰ290100 )\add*.
